An alternate numeral system specifically designed for working with numbers digitally, that takes into account the limitations of human memory and visualization skills. 

Numeral systems are a means of *organizing symbols* so that the symbol's form conveys,*at a glance*, important attributes of the signified, and can be used in concert with a [set of heuristics] to quickly derive properties of the signified. In a limited sense,?they are operating systems for getting at properties of quantities?,  